from a user's Letterboxd export.

## Features
- Upload Letterboxd ZIP export
- Rewatch & comfort movie stats
- Busiest month analysis
- Watchlist insights
- (Coming soon) IMDb enrichment: genres, runtime, actors
- (Coming soon) ML taste clustering & AI summaries

## Tech Stack
- Backend: FastAPI, Pandas
- Frontend: React / Next.js (planned)
- Data: Letterboxd export, IMDb datasets

